===Noun===
'''[[new]] [[math]]'''

# {{pejorative}} The methodology used to arrive at an unreasonably incorrect answer for a [[math]]ematical calculation.
#:''She quickly calculated the tip to be $45.00 on the restaurant tab of $110.50, apparently using '''new math'''.''